So grab the chance to get this CD… or masturbate further on torrents not having the Original with excellent dirty Black Metal sound and tons of gloomy images in enormous faded as in autumn booklet…500 copies, which ARE NOT FOR EVERYONE FOR SURE!

name: AENAON / STIELAS STORHETT "ER/Alter Ego" 7"EP-Split
description: 7'' EP split of truly exceptional bands - AENAON (Greece) and STIELAS STORHETT (Russia). On this split AENAON presents an exclusive track "Er". The origins of the track go to the ancient myth. Mathematical Chaos and Magic have turned into the incredibly beautiful canvas on this track. The exclusive epic and speedy track "Alter Ego" from STIELAS STORHETT blows the coals of the triumphant Northern Flame. Classic black 7''EP in color cardboard-sleeve including inlay containing song lyrics. 300 hand-numbered copies. Check it at www.7split.com
